                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7760" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1946</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1085 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">多方共赢：宏图公司创办惠民工厂的商业逻辑</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Multi-win-win: The Business Logic of Hongtu Company&#39;s Establishment of Huimin Factory</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">黄昶生，李虹霖，徐晶，陈实，杨爽</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国石油大学（华东）</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">青岛宏图人力资源有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规划计划部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">多方共赢；商业逻辑；乡村振兴；惠民工厂</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Multi-win-win；business logic；rural revitalization；Huimin factory</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">青岛宏图人力资源有限公司作为一家劳务派遣公司，面对产业企业“用工荒”的难题，公司发展遇到了瓶颈。正逢国家注重乡村振兴、鼓励企业产业助农的政策背景，面对企业“用工荒”、产业助农“路径窄”，我国农业机械化带来的农民“闲多忙少”，乡镇产业难发展的现实状况，总经理吴志刚响应国家与地方政府号召，积极投身乡村振兴、提高农民收入的事业，决定依托西海岸新区的第二产业丰富，利用当地农村富余劳动力，着力解决产业 “用工荒”与增进农民创收问题，形成以工厂车间外迁、农民家门口就业的 “乡村惠民工厂”商业思路，创建“乡村惠民工厂”商业模式，实现了政府、农村、农民、产业、劳务公司的多方共赢。本案例通过描述吴志刚响应国家政策、了解多方需求，建立并推广乡村惠民工厂，探索自己的商业逻辑的过程。帮助学习者了解、掌握商业逻辑的内涵，学会分析企业发展内外部环境、多主体介入的逻辑等，为企业形成自己的商业逻辑提供启发。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As a labor dispatch company, Qingdao Hongtu Human Resources Co., Ltd. has encountered a bottleneck in its development in the face of the problem of &quot;labor shortage&quot; of industrial enterprises. At the same time as the national policy background of paying attention to rural revitalization and encouraging enterprises to help farmers, facing the &quot;labor shortage&quot; of enterprises and the &quot;narrow path&quot; of industrial assistance to farmers, the reality that farmers brought about by China&#39;s agricultural mechanization are &quot;idle and busy&quot;, and it is difficult for township industries to develop, General Manager Wu Zhigang responded to the call of the national and local governments, actively engaged in the cause of rural revitalization and improving farmers&#39; income, and decided to rely on the enrichment of the secondary industry in the West Coast New Area, make use of the surplus labor force in the local countryside, and focus on solving the problem of industrial &quot;labor shortage&quot; and increasing farmers&#39; income. It has formed the business idea of &quot;Huimin factory&quot; with the factory workshop relocating and the farmers working at the doorstep, and created the business model of &quot;rural benefiting the people&quot; to achieve a win-win situation for the government, rural areas, farmers, industries and labor service companies. This case describes the process of Wu Zhigang responding to national policies, understanding the needs of various parties, establishing and promoting Huimin factories, and exploring his own business logic. Help learners understand and master the connotation of business logic, learn to analyze the internal and external environment of enterprise development, the logic of multi-subject intervention, etc., and provide inspiration for enterprises to form their own business logic.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《企业社会责任》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">商业逻辑；价值共创</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
